msgid ""
"Frequently asked questions about choosing, installing, developing, "
"deploying, and operating Klein for Ray."
msgstr "关于选择、安装、开发、部署和运维 Klein for Ray 的常见问题。"

msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "常见问题"

msgid ""
"This page gives short answers and sends you to the authoritative guide "
"for details."
msgstr "本页提供简短回答，并引导你前往权威指南了解详情。"

msgid "Choosing Klein"
msgstr "选择 Klein"

msgid "When should I use Klein?"
msgstr "何时应该使用 Klein？"

msgid ""
"Use Klein when a Ray application needs long-running record processing, "
"event time, managed keyed state, or checkpoint recovery. For bounded "
"preparation, inference, or training ingest without those semantics, use "
"Ray Data directly. See [Key concepts](key-concepts.md) and [Ray Data "
"interoperability](ray-data-interop.md)."
msgstr ""
"当 Ray 应用需要长期运行的逐记录处理、事件时间、托管键控状态或 checkpoint 恢复时，请使用 "
"Klein。对于不需要这些语义的有界数据准备、推理或训练数据摄取，请直接使用 Ray Data。请参阅[关键概念](key-"
"concepts.md)和 [Ray Data 互操作](ray-data-interop.md)。"

msgid "Is Klein part of the Ray project?"
msgstr "Klein 是 Ray 项目的一部分吗？"

msgid ""
"No. Klein is independent alpha software. The `ray.klein` namespace is a "
"technical integration point; Klein does not replace Ray's package or "
"claim Ray project endorsement. See [Architecture](architecture.md)."
msgstr ""
"不是。Klein 是独立的 Alpha 软件。`ray.klein` 命名空间是技术集成点；Klein 不会替换 Ray 包，也不声称得到 Ray"
" 项目认可。请参阅[架构](architecture.md)。"

msgid "Is Klein a drop-in replacement for Apache Flink?"
msgstr "Klein 可以直接替代 Apache Flink 吗？"

msgid ""
"No. It offers familiar DataStream, event-time, checkpoint, keyed-state, "
"and dynamic-table concepts on Ray, but its API and supported operators "
"are not a complete Flink compatibility layer. Check [Known "
"limitations](limitations.md), [operator compatibility](operator-"
"compatibility.md), and [SQL](sql.md) before porting a job."
msgstr ""
"不可以。Klein 在 Ray 上提供熟悉的 DataStream、事件时间、checkpoint、键控状态和动态表概念，但其 API "
"和受支持算子并不是完整的 Flink 兼容层。迁移作业前，请查看[已知限制](limitations.md)、[算子兼容性](operator-"
"compatibility.md)和 [SQL](sql.md)。"

msgid "Is the API stable enough for production?"
msgstr "API 是否足够稳定，可用于生产？"

msgid ""
"Klein is at `0.1.0.dev0` and classified as alpha. Production evaluation "
"should pin Klein and Ray, rehearse recovery, and accept that APIs and "
"checkpoint formats can change before 1.0. See [API stability](api-"
"stability.md) and the [production-readiness checklist](production-"
"readiness.md)."
msgstr ""
"Klein 当前版本为 `0.1.0.dev0`，并被归类为 Alpha。生产评估应固定 Klein 和 Ray 版本、演练恢复，并接受 API "
"和 checkpoint 格式可能在 1.0 前发生变化。请参阅 [API 稳定性](api-stability.md)和[生产就绪检查清单"
"](production-readiness.md)。"

msgid "Can one application mix Klein and native Ray libraries?"
msgstr "一个应用可以混用 Klein 和原生 Ray 库吗？"

msgid ""
"Yes. Bounded Klein graphs lower to Ray Data, while native streaming "
"operators run on Ray Core. Use the explicit `.data` adapter for Ray Data "
"operations and review where execution semantics change in [Ray Data "
"interoperability](ray-data-interop.md)."
msgstr ""
"可以。有界 Klein 计算图会降低为 Ray Data，而原生流算子运行在 Ray Core 上。请通过显式 `.data` 适配器执行 Ray"
" Data 操作，并在 [Ray Data 互操作](ray-data-interop.md)中查看执行语义发生变化的边界。"

msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

msgid "Which Python and Ray versions are supported?"
msgstr "支持哪些 Python 和 Ray 版本？"

msgid ""
"Python 3.10–3.12 and `ray[data]>=2.56.1,<2.57`. The Ray upper bound is "
"intentional. See [Installation](installation.md#supported-environment) "
"and [Compatibility](compatibility.md)."
msgstr ""
"支持 Python 3.10–3.12 和 `ray[data]>=2.56.1,<2.57`。Ray "
"的上界是有意设置的。请参阅[安装](installation.md#supported-"
"environment)和[兼容性](compatibility.md)。"

msgid "Can I install `ray-klein` from PyPI?"
msgstr "可以从 PyPI 安装 `ray-klein` 吗？"

msgid ""
"The current documentation does not assume a published PyPI distribution. "
"Install a source checkout non-editably, use an editable checkout for "
"development, or install a wheel built from a reviewed checkout. See "
"[Installation](installation.md#regular-installation-from-a-checkout)."
msgstr ""
"当前文档不假定 PyPI 上已有发布的发行包。你可以非 editable 方式安装源码 checkout、使用 editable checkout"
" 进行开发，或安装由已审核 checkout 构建的 wheel。请参阅[安装](installation.md#regular-"
"installation-from-a-checkout)。"

msgid "Which optional extra do I need?"
msgstr "我需要哪个可选 extra？"

msgid ""
"Use `kafka`, `iceberg`, `rocketmq`, `redis`, `rocksdb`, or `serve` for "
"the matching integration. `all` installs all runtime integrations; `dev` "
"also adds tests, docs, and contributor tools. The exact dependencies are "
"listed under [Optional extras](installation.md#optional-extras)."
msgstr ""
"对应的集成请使用 `kafka`、`iceberg`、`rocketmq`、`redis`、`rocksdb` 或 `serve`。`all` "
"安装所有运行时集成；`dev` 还会添加测试、文档和贡献者工具。确切依赖列在[可选 extras](installation.md"
"#optional-extras) 中。"

msgid "Must Klein be installed on every Ray worker?"
msgstr "每个 Ray worker 都必须安装 Klein 吗？"

msgid ""
"Yes. Every eligible worker needs the same Klein/Ray versions, graph "
"extras, application modules, and native dependencies. A driver's virtual "
"environment is not propagated automatically. See [cluster environment "
"consistency](installation.md#keep-the-cluster-environment-consistent)."
msgstr ""
"是。每个符合条件的 worker 都需要相同的 Klein/Ray 版本、计算图 extras、应用模块和原生依赖。driver "
"的虚拟环境不会自动传播。请参阅[集群环境一致性](installation.md#keep-the-cluster-environment-"
"consistent)。"

msgid "Why does the driver import a connector that a worker cannot import?"
msgstr "为什么 driver 能导入连接器，而 worker 无法导入？"

msgid ""
"The environments differ, or the optional extra/native library exists only"
" on the driver. Deploy one immutable image or artifact set to every node,"
" then restart the affected processes. See [installation "
"troubleshooting](installation.md#troubleshoot-installation)."
msgstr ""
"环境不一致，或者可选 extra/原生库只存在于 driver "
"上。请向每个节点部署同一个不可变镜像或同一套制品，然后重启受影响的进程。请参阅[安装故障排查](installation.md"
"#troubleshoot-installation)。"

msgid "Why does `import ray` work but `import ray.klein` fail?"
msgstr "为什么 `import ray` 成功，而 `import ray.klein` 失败？"

msgid ""
"Ray and Klein are separate distributions. Install Klein into the same "
"Python environment and verify it with `python -m pip show ray-klein`; "
"merely keeping the source checkout nearby does not extend the installed "
"`ray` package."
msgstr ""
"Ray 和 Klein 是两个独立的发行包。请将 Klein 安装到同一个 Python 环境中，并使用 `python -m pip show "
"ray-klein` 验证；仅将源码 checkout 放在旁边不会扩展已安装的 `ray` 包。"

msgid "Batch and streaming execution"
msgstr "批处理与流处理执行"

msgid "How does `auto` choose an execution mode?"
msgstr "`auto` 如何选择执行模式？"

msgid ""
"The whole job selects streaming when a source is unbounded, any graph "
"vertex lacks a batch lowering, or `udf.ignore-exception=true`. Only a "
"fully batch-lowerable, bounded graph with that policy disabled selects "
"batch. Selection is job-wide, not branch-by-branch. See [operator "
"compatibility](operator-compatibility.md)."
msgstr ""
"存在无界数据源、任一计算图顶点缺少批处理下沉实现，或设置 `udf.ignore-exception=true` 时，整个作业都会选择原生流处理。只有计算图有界、可完全下沉为批处理，且该策略已禁用时，才会选择批处理。该选择作用于整个作业，而不是逐分支进行。请参阅[算子兼容性](operator-"
"compatibility.md)。"

msgid "Can I force batch or streaming mode?"
msgstr "可以强制使用批处理或流处理模式吗？"

msgid ""
"Yes, set `execution.runtime.mode` to `batch` or `streaming` before "
"execution. An incompatible graph fails instead of silently changing an "
"operator's semantics. See [Configuration](configuration.md) and its "
"[reference](configuration-reference.md#execution-recovery-and-"
"checkpointing)."
msgstr ""
"可以，在执行前将 `execution.runtime.mode` 设置为 `batch` 或 "
"`streaming`。不兼容的计算图会失败，而不会悄然更改算子语义。请参阅[配置](configuration.md)及其[参考"
"](configuration-reference.md#execution-recovery-and-checkpointing)。"

msgid "How does `auto` handle a bounded custom source?"
msgstr "`auto` 如何处理有界的自定义数据源？"

msgid ""
"`SourceFunction` is a native streaming contract unless its integration "
"provides a batch lowering. A bounded custom source without that lowering "
"selects native streaming automatically; forcing batch fails. Use a Ray "
"Data source or provide a batch lowering when batch execution is required."
" See [Custom connectors](connectors/custom.md)."
msgstr ""
"除非其集成提供批处理下沉实现，否则 `SourceFunction` "
"属于原生流处理契约。缺少该下沉实现的有界自定义数据源会自动选择原生流处理；强制使用批处理将失败。需要批处理执行时，请使用 Ray Data "
"数据源或提供批处理下沉实现。请参阅[自定义连接器](connectors/custom.md)。"

msgid "Do all `DataStream` methods work in both modes?"
msgstr "所有 `DataStream` 方法都能在两种模式下工作吗？"

msgid ""
"No. Basic row transforms work in both, but keyed state, watermarks, "
"windows, and most custom source/sink contracts are streaming features; "
"many `.data` operations are batch-only. Use the [operator compatibility "
"matrix](operator-compatibility.md)."
msgstr ""
"不能。基础行转换在两种模式下都可用，但键控状态、水位线、窗口以及大多数自定义 source/sink 契约属于流处理功能；许多 `.data` "
"操作仅支持批处理。请查看[算子兼容性矩阵](operator-compatibility.md)。"

msgid "What is interactive mode?"
msgstr "什么是交互模式？"

msgid ""
"It is a deprecated, opt-in compatibility mode in which terminal "
"operations such as `take_all()` execute a bounded graph immediately. New "
"code should keep terminal operations lazy, register every intended sink, "
"call `execute(\"job-name\")`, and retrieve results from the returned job "
"handle. See [Getting started](getting-started.md)."
msgstr ""
"这是一种已弃用、需主动启用的兼容模式，其中 `take_all()` 等终端操作会立即执行有界计算图。新代码应让终端操作保持惰性，注册每个预期的 "
"sink，调用 `execute(\"job-name\")`，再从返回的作业句柄中获取结果。请参阅[快速开始](getting-"
"started.md)。"

msgid "Does local debug mode validate distributed behavior?"
msgstr "本地调试模式会验证分布式行为吗？"

msgid ""
"No. It is useful for deterministic development but does not validate Ray "
"serialization, scheduling, isolation, actor failure, or recovery. Run the"
" integration suite or a real cluster before deployment; see [Local "
"debug](local_debug.rst)."
msgstr ""
"不会。它有助于确定性开发，但不会验证 Ray 序列化、调度、隔离、actor "
"故障或恢复。部署前请运行集成套件或使用真实集群；请参阅[本地调试](local_debug.rst)。"

msgid "What is Klein's general delivery guarantee?"
msgstr "Klein 的一般交付保证是什么？"

msgid ""
"At least once. End-to-end behavior is the weakest boundary among the "
"source, state/checkpoint path, replay, and sink; selected sinks offer "
"checkpoint-transactional visibility. See [Delivery and consistency"
"](delivery-semantics.md)."
msgstr ""
"至少一次。端到端行为取决于 source、状态/checkpoint 路径、重放和 sink 中最弱的边界；部分 sink 提供 "
"checkpoint 事务可见性。请参阅[交付与一致性](delivery-semantics.md)。"

msgid "State and event time"
msgstr "状态与事件时间"

msgid "Is managed state durable by itself?"
msgstr "托管状态本身是持久的吗？"

msgid ""
"No. Memory and RocksDB are working-state backends. Recovery across node "
"or cluster loss depends on completed checkpoints in shared durable "
"storage. Ray Object Store caching accelerates recovery but is not the "
"durability boundary. See [Ray-native state](ray-native-state.md) and "
"[checkpoint storage](checkpoint-storage.md)."
msgstr ""
"不是。Memory 和 RocksDB 是工作状态后端。节点或集群丢失后的恢复依赖共享持久存储中的已完成 checkpoint。Ray "
"Object Store 缓存可以加速恢复，但不是持久性边界。请参阅 [Ray 原生状态](ray-native-state.md)和 "
"[checkpoint 存储](checkpoint-storage.md)。"

msgid "Do checkpoints make every sink exactly once?"
msgstr "Checkpoint 会让每个 sink 都实现精确一次吗？"

msgid ""
"No. An external sink may accept an effect that is replayed after failure."
" Filesystem, Iceberg append, and a correctly implemented two-phase-commit"
" sink have stronger checkpoint-transactional visibility; other sinks can "
"remain at least once. See the [sink guarantee table](delivery-"
"semantics.md#sink-behavior)."
msgstr ""
"不会。外部 sink 可能已接受某项操作效果，而该效果会在故障后重放。文件系统、Iceberg append 和正确实现的两阶段提交 sink "
"具有更强的 checkpoint 事务可见性；其他 sink 仍可能是至少一次。请参阅 [sink 保证表](delivery-"
"semantics.md#sink-behavior)。"

msgid "Why does an event-time window never emit?"
msgstr "为什么事件时间窗口始终不发出结果？"

msgid ""
"Usually one active physical input has not advanced its watermark. Assign "
"timestamps and watermarks, configure idleness for quiet inputs, and "
"inspect watermark metrics. See [Event time](event-time.md) and "
"[Troubleshooting](troubleshooting.md#windows-never-emit)."
msgstr ""
"通常是某个活跃物理输入尚未推进其水位线。请分配时间戳和水位线，为无数据输入配置空闲检测，并检查水位线指标。请参阅[事件时间](event-"
"time.md)和[故障排查](troubleshooting.md#windows-never-emit)。"

msgid "Are event timestamps seconds or milliseconds?"
msgstr "事件时间戳使用秒还是毫秒？"

msgid ""
"Non-negative integer milliseconds. Floating-point, negative, or second-"
"based values are invalid or produce the wrong window scale. Watermarks "
"must advance separately from timestamp assignment."
msgstr "使用非负整数毫秒值。浮点数、负数或以秒为单位的值无效，或者会产生错误的窗口尺度。水位线必须独立于时间戳分配向前推进。"

msgid "How do I prevent state from growing forever?"
msgstr "如何防止状态无限增长？"

msgid ""
"Choose finite windows where appropriate, configure state TTL for long-"
"lived keyed or SQL state, and monitor managed-state size. TTL is a "
"correctness choice: expired state can make later results incomplete. See "
"[Ray-native state](ray-native-state.md) and [Performance tuning"
"](performance-tuning.md)."
msgstr ""
"在适当场景选择有限窗口，为长期存在的键控状态或 SQL 状态配置状态 TTL，并监控托管状态大小。TTL "
"是一项正确性选择：过期状态可能使后续结果不完整。请参阅 [Ray 原生状态](ray-native-state.md)和[性能调优"
"](performance-tuning.md)。"

msgid "Can I change operator parallelism without losing keyed state?"
msgstr "可以在不丢失键控状态的情况下更改算子并行度吗？"

msgid ""
"Supported running operators can move managed state by key group through "
"the barrier-aligned rescale procedure. Do not change `state.keyed.max-"
"parallelism` for checkpoints that must remain restorable. Sources and "
"some sink types have additional restrictions. See [operator rescaling"
"](operator-rescaling.md)."
msgstr ""
"受支持的运行中算子可以通过 barrier 对齐的 rescale 流程按 key group 移动托管状态。对于必须保持可恢复的 "
"checkpoint，不要更改 `state.keyed.max-parallelism`。Source 和某些 sink "
"类型还有额外限制。请参阅[算子 rescale](operator-rescaling.md)。"

msgid "What survives total Ray cluster loss?"
msgstr "Ray 集群完全丢失后，哪些内容能够保留？"

msgid ""
"Detached actors do not. Resubmit the graph and restore from shared "
"durable checkpoint storage. Record the code version, namespace, source "
"identity, checkpoint path, and max parallelism needed for recovery; see "
"[checkpoint recovery](checkpoint-recovery.md)."
msgstr ""
"Detached actor 无法保留。请重新提交计算图，并从共享持久 checkpoint "
"存储恢复。记录恢复所需的代码版本、命名空间、source 标识、checkpoint 路径和最大并行度；请参阅 [checkpoint 恢复"
"](checkpoint-recovery.md)。"

msgid "SQL and connectors"
msgstr "SQL 与连接器"

msgid "Which engine executes Klein SQL?"
msgstr "哪个引擎执行 Klein SQL？"

msgid ""
"SQLGlot parses one AST. Bounded queries lower to Ray Dataset operations; "
"continuous queries lower to native Klein operators with managed state and"
" changelog rows. Klein does not embed DuckDB. See [SQL and Table "
"connectors](sql.md)."
msgstr ""
"SQLGlot 解析统一的 AST。有界查询降低为 Ray Dataset 操作；连续查询降低为带托管状态和 changelog 行的原生 "
"Klein 算子。Klein 不嵌入 DuckDB。请参阅 [SQL 与 Table 连接器](sql.md)。"

msgid "Is every SQL query supported in streaming mode?"
msgstr "流处理模式支持所有 SQL 查询吗？"

msgid ""
"No. Streaming SQL implements a documented subset and rejects unsupported "
"forms with `SQLQueryError` rather than silently changing semantics. "
"Stateful joins, aggregates, and Top-N also require bounded state "
"planning. Review the SQL guide and [known limitations](limitations.md"
"#sql-and-dynamic-tables)."
msgstr ""
"不支持。流式 SQL 实现已记录的子集，并通过 `SQLQueryError` 拒绝不受支持的形式，而不会悄然更改语义。有状态 join、聚合和 "
"Top-N 也需要有界状态规划。请查看 SQL 指南和[已知限制](limitations.md#sql-and-dynamic-tables)。"

msgid "Why does a top-level SQL query not see a table I created earlier?"
msgstr "为什么顶层 SQL 查询看不到之前创建的表？"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"`ray.klein.sql()` creates a fresh one-query session. Use "
"`ray.klein.execute_sql()` for a persistent module-level catalog, or pass "
"explicit `tables={...}` bindings. See [Choose a SQL entry "
"point](sql.md#choose-a-sql-entry-point)."
msgstr ""
"`ray.klein.sql()` 会创建全新的单查询 session。若要使用持久的模块级 catalog，请使用 "
"`ray.klein.execute_sql()`，或传递显式 `tables={...}` 绑定。请参阅[选择 SQL "
"入口点](sql.md#choose-a-sql-entry-point)。"

msgid "Which connectors are built in?"
msgstr "内置了哪些连接器？"

msgid ""
"Ray Data, collections, Kafka, RocketMQ, Canal JSON, filesystems, Iceberg,"
" Redis, console, custom connectors, and Ray Serve integration are "
"documented in the [connector catalog](connectors/index.md). Their "
"batch/streaming modes and extras differ."
msgstr ""
"[连接器目录](connectors/index.md)记录了 Ray Data、集合、Kafka、RocketMQ、Canal "
"JSON、文件系统、Iceberg、Redis、控制台、自定义连接器和 Ray Serve 集成。它们支持的批处理/流处理模式和 extras "
"各不相同。"

msgid "Does a Table DDL connector create external infrastructure?"
msgstr "Table DDL 连接器会创建外部基础设施吗？"

msgid ""
"No. `CREATE TABLE` validates logical schema and connector options; it "
"does not create topics, brokers, buckets, or databases. External "
"resources and credentials must already exist."
msgstr ""
"不会。`CREATE TABLE` 会验证逻辑 schema 和连接器选项，但不会创建 topic、broker、bucket "
"或数据库。外部资源和凭据必须已存在。"

msgid "Can I add a connector outside the core package?"
msgstr "可以在核心包之外添加连接器吗？"

msgid ""
"Yes. Implement the source/sink contracts or a `TableFactory`. Third-party"
" packages can publish table factories through the "
"`ray.klein.table_factories` entry-point group. See [Custom "
"connectors](connectors/custom.md)."
msgstr ""
"可以。请实现 source/sink 契约或 `TableFactory`。第三方包可以通过 "
"`ray.klein.table_factories` 入口点组发布 table "
"factory。请参阅[自定义连接器](connectors/custom.md)。"

msgid "Where do I find connector delivery guarantees and schemas?"
msgstr "在哪里查找连接器交付保证和 schema？"

msgid ""
"Each connector page documents its input/output shape and recovery "
"boundary; the cross-connector summary is [Delivery and consistency "
"guarantees](delivery-semantics.md). Do not infer exactly-once behavior "
"from checkpointing alone."
msgstr ""
"每个连接器页面都记录其输入/输出形态和恢复边界；跨连接器摘要位于[交付与一致性保证](delivery-semantics.md)。不要仅凭启用了"
" checkpoint 就推断具备精确一次行为。"

msgid "Deployment and operations"
msgstr "部署与运维"

msgid "How should I submit a production job?"
msgstr "应该如何提交生产作业？"

msgid ""
"Build one immutable driver/worker environment, initialize the intended "
"Ray cluster explicitly, and submit a normal Python entry point through "
"the cluster's Ray Jobs or platform workflow. Use shared checkpoint "
"storage and record the returned Klein namespace. See "
"[Deployment](deployment.md) and the [production streaming walkthrough"
"](production-streaming.md)."
msgstr ""
"构建统一的不可变 driver/worker 环境，显式初始化目标 Ray 集群，并通过集群的 Ray Jobs 或平台工作流提交普通 "
"Python 入口点。使用共享 checkpoint 存储，并记录返回的 Klein "
"命名空间。请参阅[部署](deployment.md)和[生产流处理演练](production-streaming.md)。"

msgid "Does the job stop when the submitting process exits?"
msgstr "提交进程退出时，作业会停止吗？"

msgid ""
"Not for native streaming execution: its `JobManager` and workers are "
"detached actors. A new client can discover and manage them. Loss of the "
"whole Ray cluster still requires resubmission from durable state; see "
"[driver fault tolerance](driver-fault-tolerance.md)."
msgstr ""
"原生流处理执行不会停止：其 `JobManager` 和 worker 都是 detached actor。新客户端可以发现并管理它们。整个 "
"Ray 集群丢失后，仍需从持久状态重新提交；请参阅 [driver 容错](driver-fault-tolerance.md)。"

msgid "Why can the CLI not find my job?"
msgstr "为什么 CLI 找不到我的作业？"

msgid ""
"Confirm `RAY_ADDRESS` selects the correct cluster and copy the exact "
"namespace from `ray-klein list --all --json`. A Ray Jobs submission ID, a"
" job display name, a state API job ID, and the Klein Ray namespace are "
"not universally interchangeable. See [CLI identifiers](cli-reference.md"
"#job-names-namespaces-and-job-ids)."
msgstr ""
"确认 `RAY_ADDRESS` 选择了正确集群，并从 `ray-klein list --all --json` 复制准确的命名空间。Ray "
"Jobs 提交 ID、作业显示名称、状态 API 作业 ID 和 Klein Ray 命名空间并非在所有场景下都可互换。请参阅 [CLI 标识符"
"](cli-reference.md#job-names-namespaces-and-job-ids)。"

msgid "Does Ctrl+C in `attach` stop the job?"
msgstr "在 `attach` 中按 Ctrl+C 会停止作业吗？"

msgid ""
"No. It detaches the terminal view and leaves the job running. Use `ray-"
"klein cancel NAMESPACE --force` or the equivalent `stop` alias for "
"deliberate cancellation. See [CLI reference](cli-reference.md#attach)."
msgstr ""
"不会。它只会解除终端视图的附加，作业仍会继续运行。如需主动取消，请使用 `ray-klein cancel NAMESPACE --force` "
"或等效的 `stop` 别名。请参阅 [CLI 参考](cli-reference.md#attach)。"

msgid "Is the Klein Dashboard safe to expose publicly?"
msgstr "可以安全地公开暴露 Klein Dashboard 吗？"

msgid ""
"No. Its control endpoint is unauthenticated. It binds to loopback by "
"default and refuses a non-loopback listener unless `--allow-"
"unauthenticated` is explicit; that flag is not a security mechanism. Use "
"a tunnel or a protected proxy and follow [Security](security.md)."
msgstr ""
"不可以。其控制端点没有身份验证。默认绑定回环地址；除非显式指定 `--allow-"
"unauthenticated`，否则会拒绝非回环监听器，而该标志本身并不是安全机制。请使用隧道或受保护的代理，并遵循[安全](security.md)指南。"

msgid "How do I monitor a running job?"
msgstr "如何监控运行中的作业？"

msgid ""
"Use `ray-klein status`, the bundled Dashboard, structured logs, Ray "
"metrics, and durable checkpoint history. The full signals and Prometheus "
"examples are in [Observability](observability.md); use `status --json` or"
" the Python state API for automation."
msgstr ""
"使用 `ray-klein status`、随附的 Dashboard、结构化日志、Ray 指标和持久 checkpoint 历史。完整信号和 "
"Prometheus 示例请参阅[可观测性](observability.md)；自动化请使用 `status --json` 或 Python "
"状态 API。"

msgid "How do I diagnose low throughput or backpressure?"
msgstr "如何诊断低吞吐量或反压？"

msgid ""
"Start with per-operator input/output, processing latency, buffer "
"utilization, backpressure duration, source lag, checkpoint time, and Ray "
"node resources. Tune one boundary at a time using [Performance tuning"
"](performance-tuning.md) and the symptom guide in "
"[Troubleshooting](troubleshooting.md)."
msgstr ""
"首先检查各算子的输入/输出、处理延迟、缓冲区利用率、反压时长、source lag、checkpoint 耗时和 Ray 节点资源。按照[性能调优"
"](performance-tuning.md)和[故障排查](troubleshooting.md)中的症状指南，每次只调整一个边界。"

msgid "How do I upgrade a stateful job?"
msgstr "如何升级有状态作业？"

msgid ""
"Create and record a completed durable checkpoint, stop the old job, "
"deploy one reviewed environment, restore explicitly, and validate source "
"position, state, sink behavior, and a new checkpoint. Do not assume "
"automatic checkpoint-schema migration; follow [Upgrade Klein "
"jobs](upgrading.md)."
msgstr ""
"创建并记录一个已完成的持久 checkpoint，停止旧作业，部署已审核的环境，显式恢复，并验证 source 位置、状态、sink 行为和新 "
"checkpoint。不要假定 checkpoint schema 会自动迁移；请遵循[升级 Klein 作业](upgrading.md)。"

msgid "What should I include in a support report?"
msgstr "支持请求中应该包含哪些信息？"

msgid ""
"Include the Klein, Ray, and Python versions; plan; namespace; explicit "
"configuration with secrets removed; first traceback; relevant component "
"logs; checkpoint history; and a small metric window around the failure. "
"See [Collect a useful report](troubleshooting.md#collect-a-useful-report)"
" and use the private process in `SECURITY.md` for suspected "
"vulnerabilities."
msgstr ""
"请提供 Klein、Ray 和 Python 版本、执行计划、命名空间、已移除 secret 的显式配置、第一个 "
"traceback、相关组件日志、checkpoint "
"历史，以及故障前后的一小段指标窗口。请参阅[收集有用的报告](troubleshooting.md#collect-a-useful-"
"report)；若怀疑存在漏洞，请使用 `SECURITY.md` 中的私密报告流程。"

#~ msgid "Why must a bounded custom source sometimes select streaming explicitly?"
#~ msgstr "为什么有界自定义 source 有时必须显式选择流处理？"
